Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比邻星之冠」已经连接成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认能量导管联机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除持有第2类技术资格证以外的作业员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快退入附近的居住区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 杜鹃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认报酬了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷欧帕罗特之间的恩怨就这样了结了吧 弁庆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 波拿帕罗特那家伙 到底要纠结我的太阳能镜到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也不难理解 因为毕竟是我的太阳能镜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在先让他们远离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂总帅 已经刻不容缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去救那些被抓住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况已经改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们和弁庆一起回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval现在应该从超时空跳跃的反应中推算出这个宙域了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被跟踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在责怪你们 你们回来真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奥君 殖民地内的非战斗人员全部都到避难所去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以战斗状态准备迎击 同时进行雷欧帕罗特的修复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「剑」的搜索呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们负责寻找那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯藏起来的「剑」只有风魔能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用B.O.A.R.SHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老 非常抱歉这么紧急…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你们没事真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能回到这里是托了那边的年轻人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹子的福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高岭！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:35.00,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}密剑 闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁庆那家伙 竟然割了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叛徒 竟然叛变到叛乱军去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许可他四处旅行的是我 也许那正是他所追寻的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中发生什么 有必要追查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在的问题是雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比邻星之冠」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就舍弃的据点现在要用来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是想要取回来 50年前的那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Enigma已经在我们这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美的情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她在Enigma 睡在那个孩子旁边了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有生命危险 但总是醒不来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.高岭不回来的理由就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美已经觉醒了 她本来所拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-QT？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是可以反转QT的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval是知道这个所以把奈美…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从神乐大人那里继承的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看透一切的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才的头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-QT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然最后的钥匙还是狮子堂秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让雷欧帕罗特把力量取回了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说将成为无法挽回的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库桑齐贝 破坏雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在修复中 现在追击他应该无力反击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.阿蕾达 把Existent-Z交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将狮子堂秋叶带来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval一定会以秋叶为目标攻来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高岭 你来保护秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 姐姐 我被Nerval…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不全是坏事 多亏这样敌人的内情现在全清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔什么的 就用你的剑来抹去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧帕罗特的修复完成后 就采取攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 右转舵 Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将喷射器掘出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是点火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的东西要拿来做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像昨天吃过的那个呢 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 炸鯵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 觉得肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧帕罗特的秘密兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是埋在陨石中 用纳米机器人修理过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但竟然是必须用探宝棒来找 灵异科甘拜下风了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 Nerval他们的机器是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业工程 从A8到V21全部省略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「剑」展开后 立即实装
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部的调整推迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人攻过来之前不知能不能完工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是…那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 妹子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…不在了的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法相信！怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站是雷欧帕罗特站前 雷欧帕罗特站前！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站是…下站是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘本真好呢 好象心灵都被洗涤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是没变 在做些蠢事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有轨电车 是你干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好久没来这里了 也好久没见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 说起来是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天房间太安静了 我完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们不在…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮芋头怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…说是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那个煮芋头死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直让我很不爽 成天毒舌我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样从今天开始我就可以高枕无忧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说死了的人已经死了 这有什么不对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央监视台检测出大规模的空间歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人工智能殖民地！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全作业员暂时撤退 迎击部队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次见面都发现你越来越穷酸了 雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了 等会再收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得先抓到小秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库桑齐贝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要立即实行修复作业 你们负责掩护B.O.A.R.SHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库桑齐贝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…小秋叶在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越宇宙的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会将秋叶交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高岭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们…最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风音小姐 请看这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经攻入市内了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地点传给你了 拜托你保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这是我们的机体吧 乌鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还标着「ICP试用机」的话太不够威猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于同你再次对战我无比遗憾 Miss.高岭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi~ 住在雷欧帕罗特里面的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住秋叶的人会得到最高级的箱子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…Existent-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 秋叶前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 狮子堂 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音音子…菲里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月！我要进箱子里！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂 如果你进入箱子就正中Nerval的下怀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…进入箱子里就会忘记讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子的事也全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是穿越宇宙的少女吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没了我就无法打倒Nerval吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶和妹子不都是真心…真心的关怀对方的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你如果忘记了妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那种过分的事…不是我喜欢的秋叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请站起来吧 秋叶 也为了妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙…鯵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蜜 那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民用机？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没有武装在外面晃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被击落的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 将我们送到雷欧帕罗特那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又来上访了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可已经克服了你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军了 雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小秋叶的事完了之后我会好好疼爱你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用对人工智能攻击模式 哦呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲里奥？音音子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧 我带QT-Rose来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯博士！你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么糟糕种子就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样Existent-Z的QT就不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少道个谢啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 保护秋叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have control！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进行对接作业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一太阳能镜停止在对接位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来开始实行第一轮连接作业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完工并向第二太阳能镜移动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在QT-Rose的有效圈内 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二太阳能镜开始连接作业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完工后立即向第三太阳能镜移动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在抓住那小姑娘前不能好好的教训雷欧帕罗特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶由我来保护！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶去雷欧帕罗特那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机体是…穗乃香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神凪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三太阳能镜连接完成 雷欧帕罗特修复完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全作业人员请立即从最近的入口退避到雷欧帕罗特殖民地里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于把所有部件全取回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧帕罗特修复 全工程完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业人员避难也完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让先头部队也全部撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧帕罗特 用「剑」一口气把帐清算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真的好好连接上了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳能镜不能用 唉…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯说了 雷欧帕罗特的「剑」上有封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解放雷欧帕罗特的力量的 只用黄金枪和秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说妹子的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我将你卷入命运之中 也许妹子不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不打倒Nerval 还会有重要的人受伤死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止Nerval 秋叶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我会保护秋叶 连着妹子的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会的 秋叶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月…穗乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那装束是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是能勾起我想欺负你的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来解除你的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说封印？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 穿越宇宙的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 认为自己一直没有明白和Nerval战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…只有我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你做到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你得逞吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的 和大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！雷欧帕罗特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卸装！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？这才是我的真正姿态！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库桑齐贝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把律师叫过来 我要行使沉默权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你 妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 即使这么做…妹子也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子不会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 妹子…妹子…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你刚才说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀的？别说些容易引起误会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个煮芋头还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Nerval大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:14.65,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(502,310)}终结的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判长 被告库桑齐贝是无罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判员 说下意见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有罪吗？总觉得那个人很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也是这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我抗议！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:58.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡はいつでもそばにある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:08.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝きたいよ　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:24.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの中　騒めくノイズは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:31.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馴れ愛の束縛　動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:38.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しみが散らばる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探して　失い、また求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:49.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿って　わたしの糸を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡は必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:03:01.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと抱いてあげる　一雫の痛みも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯った証が　星になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:14.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扉をあけて　飛べるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:58.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹一直就在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:08.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要发光 照亮未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:24.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中的 凌乱的杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:31.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已熟知的爱的束缚 …动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:38.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦遍布着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找着… 失去，然后再次追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:49.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追溯吧 沿着我的轨迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹必然会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:03:01.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地将你抱住 不让你有一点疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮的证明 成为了恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:14.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开门扉吧… 飞向天空！
